<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Netflix Music</title>

    
    <!-- Jquery -->
    <script defer src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.3.js" integrity="sha256-nQLuAZGRRcILA+6dMBOvcRh5Pe310sBpanc6+QBmyVM=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <!-- favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" />
    
    <!-- FontAwsome -->
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c37ef34cf6.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>

    <!-- BOOTSTRAP -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <!-- ICONS -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@48,400,1,0"
    />
    
    <!-- INTRO JS -->
    <script defer src="/js/introJS.js"></script>
    <!-- main js -->
    <script defer src="/js/main.js"></script>
    <!-- HEADER JS -->
    <script defer src="/js/header.js"></script>
    <!-- modal js -->
    <script defer src="/js/modal.js"></script>
    <!-- swiper -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://unpkg.com/swiper@8/swiper-bundle.min.css"
    />
    <script
      defer
      src="https://unpkg.com/swiper@8/swiper-bundle.min.js"
    ></script>
    <script defer src="/js/swiper.js"></script>
    <script defer src="/js/mainBannerMVSwiper.js"></script>



    <!-- main css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/media.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mediaHeaderVideo.css" />

  </head>
  <body style="overflow-x: hidden;">
    <!-- header -->
    <header>
      <div class="inner">
        <!-- 로고 -->
        <a class="header__logo" href="#">
          <img
            src="/img/netflix_logo/nav_logo/netflixMusic_logo@2x.png"
            alt="로고 이미지"
          />
        </a>

        <!-- MENUS -->
        <div class="menus">
          <a href="#">홈</a>
          <a href="./chart.html">차트</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 모바일용 메뉴 -->
        <div class="btn-group mobile-menus">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger dropdown-toggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
            메뉴
          </button>
          <ul class="dropdown-menu mobile-dropDownMenu">
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">홈</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="./chart.html">차트</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 서칭 및 로그인 외-->
        <div class="ex-menu">
          <input type="text" class="search" id="no-hidden" />
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="search__icon"
            ><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i
          ></a>
          <!-- 반응형 검색창체크 -->
          <a class="mobile__check"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="mobile-check">done</span></a>

          <!-- POP-UP -->
          <div href="javascript:void(0)" class="pop-up">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bell"></i>
            <div class="pop-up__contain">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="pop-up__deco"
                >arrow_drop_down</span
              >
              <div class="pop-up__board">최근 알림 메시지가 없습니다.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- LOGIN 영역 -->
          <div class="login">
            <!-- LOGIN-MOADL & POP-UP -->
            <div class="login__submenus">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="login__submenus__deco"
                >arrow_drop_down</span
              >

              <div class="login__contents__contain">
                <ul class="login__submenus__list">
                  <li class="submenus__first">
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        <div class="login-sub icon1"></div>
                        <p>프로필1</p>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <div class="login-sub icon2"></div>
                        <p>프로필2</p>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <div class="login-sub icon3"></div>
                        <p>프로필3</p>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <div class="login-sub icon4"></div>
                        <p>프로필4</p>
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>

                  <li class="submenus__second">
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="pen-icon">edit</span></a>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)">프로필 관리</a>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="switch_account">switch_account</span></a>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)">프로필 이전</a>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="account">person</span></a>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)">계정</a>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <a href="https://help.netflix.com/ko"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="question">help</span></a>
                        <a href="https://help.netflix.com/ko">고객 센터</a>
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>

                  <li class="submenus__third">
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)"><div class="logout__logo"></div></a>
                    <a class="logoout__text" href="/login">뮤직에서 로그아웃</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="login__arrow"
            >arrow_drop_down</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <!-- 색션1 메인배너 및 MV swiper-->
      <section class="section1">
        <div class="inner non-padding">
          <!-- Swiper -->
          <div class="swiper bannerSwiper">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              <% for (let i=0; i < mainBanner.length; i++) { %>
              <div class="swiper-slide mvslide">
                <div class="banner-box">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="ddd">
                  <h1 class="main-banner-title"><%= mainBanner[i].TITLE%></h1>
                  <span><%= mainBanner[i].SINGER %></span>
                  <p>
                    <%= mainBanner[i].CONTENT %>
                  </p>
                  <div class="btn-box">
                    <button class="btn btn--detail">상세 보기</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <% } %>
            </div>
            <!-- Swiper buttn -->
            <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
            <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
       
      <!-- 섹션2 장르 필터 버튼 -->
      <section class="section2">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="chart">
            <!-- <p class="main-title">실시간 차트</p> -->
            <div class="sub">
              <div class="sub__detail">
                <!-- filter BTN -->
                <ul>
                  <li class="list active" data-filter="all">All</li>
                  <li class="list" data-filter="kpop">K-POP</li>
                  <li class="list" data-filter="pop">POP</li>
                  <li class="list" data-filter="hiphop">Hip-hop</li>
                  <li class="list" data-filter="classic">Classic</li>
                  <li class="list" data-filter="dance">Dance</li>
                </ul>
                <!-- <p class="all-title">All</p> -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <div class="genre-zone"></div>
      
      <!-- 섹션3 앨범자켓 스와이퍼(재생) + 모달-->
      <section class="section3">
        <div class="inner">
          <span class="all-title">All</span>
          <div class="swiper-zone">
            <div class="swiper2 albums">
              <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                <% for(let i=0; i<album.length; i++) {%>
                <div class="swiper-slide">
                  <div class="album-box" style="background-image: url('<%=album[i].ALBUM_IMG%>');">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 앨범 Swiper btn1 -->
          <div class="swiper-button-prev mainSwiper0"></div>
          <div class="swiper-button-next mainSwiper0"></div>
        </div>
      </section>        
    </main>

    <!-- footer -->
    <footer>
      <div class="inner">
        <p class="question">질문이 있으신가요? 문의 전화: 080-000-0000</p>
        <div class="footer__menus">
          <ul>
            <li>자주 묻는 질문</li>
            <li>투자 정보(IR)</li>
            <li>개인정보 처리방침</li>
            <li>속도 테스트</li>
          </ul>
          <ul>
            <li>고객 센터</li>
            <li>입사 정보</li>
            <li>쿠키 설정</li>
            <li>법적 고지</li>
          </ul>
          <ul>
            <li>계정</li>
            <li>넷플릭스 지원 디바이스</li>
            <li>회사 정보</li>
            <li>오직 넷플릭스뮤직에서</li>
          </ul>
          <ul>
            <li>미디어 센터</li>
            <li>이용 약관</li>
            <li>문의하기</li>
          </ul> 
        </div>

        <div class="dropdown">
          <button class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i> 한국어
          </button>
          <ul class="dropdown-menu">
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">English(US)</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">English(UK)</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Japan</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">China</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">German</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">French</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Italian</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="company_info">
          넷플릭스뮤직 대한민국 <br /><br />
          넷플릭스뮤직 서비스코리아 유한회사 통신판매업신고번호: 제 2023-서울마포-0422호 전화번호: 080-000-0000 <br />
          대표: 두루미와 아이들<br />
          이메일 주소: korea@netflixmusic.com<br />
          주소: 대한민국 서울특별시 마포구 염리동 55, 코딩온 지하1층 우편번호 03100<br />
          사업자등록번호: 165-00-01010<br />
          클라우드 호스팅: Amazon Web Services Inc.<br />
          공정거래위원회 웹사이트<br />
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>


    <!-- modal -->
    <div id="modal" class="modal-overlay">
      <div class="modal-window">
        <div class="close-area">X</div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="content-image">
            <!-- <img class="image" src="img/main_album/main_album1.png" /> -->
          </div>

          <div class="content-text">
            <h2 class="al-name">ALBUM</h2>
            <div class="singer">singer</div>
            <div class="date">2020. 02. 02</div>
            <div class="info">
              IVE THE 2nd SINGLE ALBUM
            </div>
            <div class="info-sub">
              - “사랑할 용기가 있다면?” ‘감히 뛰어들어’ 큐피드가 된 아이브,
              Z세대의 사랑법 …더보기 - 데뷔 동시 ‘글로벌 수퍼 루키’, 주체적인
